{
  "stem": "22856.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I tried, of course, to improve the wages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I went through several shops, several factories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I came to the conclusion that this is not my future, that I have to continue my bookkeeping accountancy, which I knew when I was working in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And during one bar mitzvah simcha, I met one gentleman who told me that he knows somebody who would employ me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I have to see him and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took me time to decide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because in the meantime, I had to paint my accommodation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And during interval, when I looked through the I found an advert that a Jewish girl would be necessary for a small timber mill office.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the name-- the address was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I rang my friend in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said-- I knew that she has got a small child that he is parading with that pram here and there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That I had that address where I should inquire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I ask her, go there and ask the man who put the advert if instead of a Jewish girl, if he could employ a Jewish boy with the same wages what a girl.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because by that time, the girl was receiving 75% the wages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my friend went there and they say, all right, we would like to see the man, because she described as a survivor from Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I brought some credentials.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I made a good impression.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they say, all right, we employ you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the work was a little bit far from my place of residence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived by eastern Kilda.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to go by train to Richmond, change the line and go to Mitchum, which was close to Ringwood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One hour there, one hour there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
